# Pull Request

Use `gh` for all GitHub tasks.

Before creating a PR, run in parallel: `git status`, `git diff`, remote tracking check, `git log` and `git diff [base]...HEAD`.

- Push with `-u` if needed, then `gh pr create` with a HEREDOC body.
- Summarize all commits on the branch, not just the latest.
- Include Summary and Test plan sections.
- Return the PR URL when done.
